We ordered a kit for the machine and after assembling the machine, we made all the electronics ourselves.
We have been looking for a long time for a convenient set for the machine that will have many useful functions and advantages included in the set.
And in electronics, we came up with a solution to the problem of heating wires by taking thicker ones.
And to communicate between Raspberry PI camera v2.1 and Raspberry PI 4, we use the cable. And we ourselves came up with the location of sensors.
The distance sensors are located on the beginnig of vehicle to react in the time.Theu must be before the wheels
